    "answer": "Let's face it, more screen space is a good thing.<br><br>One screen can become a major bottleneck for high-performance work and your ability to structure your workflow. If you've ever worked from a single laptop screen, you'll know the pain: juggling tabs, jumping between conference calls, emails, creative apps, documents, spreadsheets, deep creative workflows and more.<br><br>That's where portable monitors come in. They give you the freedom to bring a second (or even third) screen with you, so you can recreate your desktop setup anywhere, without compromise.<br><br>We also know that having the freedom to get up, move between work locations, or even set up to get inspired in different locations, can make a world of difference to how you immerse yourself in your work.<br><br>For business travellers and professionals on the move, compromises to performance when working on the road should be minimal…. that's where espresso Displays come in.<br><br>In short, more space at your fingertips, anywhere."
